I know all arohas will agree with me on that. I also love watching them being complete crack heads and naughty sexy boys, but it's when they sing like this that they completely hook me.

I mean, I don't understand the Korean parts without a translation, but the song has definitely got enough English to convey the meaning of missing someone and yes, I miss my boyfriend, haven't been with him since February 2020, despite seeing him everyday on video calls. I also Miss MJ even though I watch him in these clips all the time.
